OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussian schoolbook urges   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fteens to fight in Ukraine  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A new Russian school textbook has been 
OL,6, produced that distorts the history of  
OL,7, the war against Ukraine and encourages 
OL,8, students to join the army.             
OL,10,FIt has been designed for a new subject 
OL,11,Fentitled "Fundamentals of Security and 
OL,12,FDefence of the Motherland".            
OL,14,FThe lesson is compulsory for high      
OL,15,Fschool students aged 15 to 18 in Russia
OL,16,Fand occupied territories in Ukraine.   
OL,18,FIt will be taught once a week from     
OL,19,FSeptember, replacing a lesson known as 
OL,20,F"Fundamentals of Safe Living".         
